Title: Enhanced Experiences for Citizens and Staff

Span.Text: Interact with citizens the way they want to using traditional and new digital channels, joined up. Staff have the right information at their fingertips to provide personalised and relevant information every time, whatever the channel.
"Working with Microsoft has helped us to build these solutions at a better price point and higher quality than would otherwise have been possible. We've saved over £10m per annum so far."
Geoff Connell, Chief Information Officer, Newham Borough Council

“I feel immensely proud of the very visible differences we’ve made since implementing Dynamics. We are now responding much faster to customers and helping them with their needs. We’re also delivering accessible, high quality & consistent services and we are being rewarded with record levels of customer satisfaction.”
Liz St Louis, Head of Customer Service & Development, Sunderland City Council

The Government Digital Strategy sets out how government will redesign its digital services to make them so straightforward and convenient that all those who can use them prefer to do so.
Microsoft solutions fulfil many of the requirements needed to support a 'Digital by Default' approach to supplying government transactional services.

Enable easier interaction with applications, provide personalised and relevant experiences that anticipate needs, remember preferences, and adapt to unique work styles, delivering quality citizen services where and when they are needed.

Gain operational efficiencies, reduce costs, and help ensure security through an integrated suite of solutions. By integrating Unified Communications and rich presence into business workflows, latency and delays can be reduced or eliminated. For geographically dispersed teams, group chat can enable efficient, topic-specific, multi-party discussions.

Automate records throughout the document lifecycle. From creation and collaboration to record declaration, policy-driven retention, and finally, document disposal or archiving, our solutions allows users to collaborate and share information securely across boundaries, protect document integrity, and reduce legal risk.
